"""RAG sysprompt rewrite (spa/xe/legal) + condense anti-coreference-drift fix.

Evidence-driven fix for two reproduced multi-turn bugs (2026-06-16 QC report):

  BUG A (spa follow-up coreference) — turn1 "tẩy da chết body", turn2
    "chi tiết về nó" → bot dumped the whole service price-list instead of
    detailing tẩy-da-chết. Root cause PINNED at the condense node: the
    condense LLM rewrote "nó" into the generic meta-phrase "dịch vụ hoặc
    sản phẩm được đề cập trước đó" (trace f288c516, adaptive_router_decomposed
    original) — a query with NO content words → retrieval pulled the generic
    CSV price-table chunk (spa-2 @0.90) → answer drift. Two compounding
    layers fixed here:
      * condense prompt (language_packs, prompt_key='condense', vi+en):
        ban generic meta-phrases, force substituting the REAL antecedent name.
      * spa system_prompt: 1-branch-per-turn + explicit follow-up=same-service
        rule so the prior turn no longer bleeds multiple services into history.

  BUG B (xe multi-variant) — same tyre spec ("265/50R20") maps to >1 product
    (CityTraxx H/P vs WildTraxx A/T) but the bot returned only ONE (whichever
    chunk ranked top). xe system_prompt MẪU TRẢ LỜI was singular. Fixed by
    porting the proven n8n COUNT_RULE: list ALL matching products, plus the
    quantity=0 ⇒ hết-hàng source-of-truth rule.

Domain-neutral note: brand sysprompt CONTENT for demo bots living in
bots.system_prompt is governed via alembic per the no-psql-hotfix rule
(same pattern as 0072 / 0214 / 0215). The domain-neutral guard only scans
*.template files, not migrations. The condense prompt stays domain-neutral
(no brand). Idempotent + reversible: downgrade restores prior content verbatim.
"""
